00:59:29.400 --> 00:59:32.440
Solo me faltan dos.

00:59:34.769 --> 00:59:35.969
Solo por un rato.

00:59:36.340 --> 00:59:37.909
¿Qué significa eso?

00:59:38.480 --> 00:59:39.539
Bueno...

00:59:40.349 --> 00:59:44.078
